Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Watanabe, the structure on your side can't hold anymore! Please move away quickly! Do you hear me, Watanabe...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Ol' pops there wants to go on an explosive suicide run!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm-hm, that's the first time Nanami's seen a human angry!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Interesting! You do deserve Nanami's seal of approval!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami knows what you're thinking. You only have to order, and Nanami will execute!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Yep! This is a once-in-a-lifetime chance! Because I normally only take orders from that eye-patched gramps!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'So, what do you say? Commandant of Gray Raven?', 4: '2'}
{2: '...Nanami, I order you to help Watanabe!', 3: '18'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hahaha! There you go! Nanami, one mission, coming up!', 4: '2'}
